                            <comment id="15748078" author="githubbot" created="Wed, 14 Dec 2016 11:23:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Github user StephanEwen commented on a diff in the pull request:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/flink/pull/2887#discussion_r92373183&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/flink/pull/2887#discussion_r92373183&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &amp;#8212; Diff: flink-runtime/src/main/java/org/apache/flink/runtime/blob/FileSystemBlobStore.java &amp;#8212;&lt;br/&gt;
    @@ -81,7 +81,7 @@ public void put(File localFile, JobID jobId, String key) throws Exception {&lt;br/&gt;
     	}&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;     	private void put(File fromFile, String toBlobPath) throws Exception {&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;try (OutputStream os = FileSystem.get(new URI(toBlobPath))&lt;br/&gt;
    +		try (OutputStream os = FileSystem.get(new Path(toBlobPath).toUri())
	&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;
		&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;End diff &amp;#8211;&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;/ul&gt;
		&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;    Would be good to avoid creating the Path twice and do `Path p = new Path(toBlobPath); p.getFileSystem().create(p, true)`&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
